 city girl?"],[4016,4170,"Stealing the show at my party?"],[4216,4341,"No way, city bitch."],[4366,4504,"I'm gonna take you down."]],"39":[[58,212,"Excuse me, everyone."],[212,316,"Just a moment."],[358,450,"I want to thank all y'all"],[450,538,"for coming to my..."],[663,788,"our,"],[788,896,"engagement party."],[1046,1134,"Oh, my god."],[1197,1305,"My engagement ring."],[1305,1376,"It's missing."],[1376,1430,"What?"],[1451,1630,"It's worth millions."],[1789,1872,"Madison."],[1901,2043,"It was you, wasn't it?"],[2093,2164,"Max, go."],[2164,2206,"Check her."],[2206,2252,"Do it."],[2277,2331,"Go!"],[2452,2502,"Hey!"],[2506,2548,"Hey!"],[2581,2635,"Let me go!"],[2635,2740,"I didn't take anything!"],[2740,2836,"We'll see about that."],[2873,2973,"Max, check her clothes."],[2973,3094,"Strip search her if you have to."],[3336,3407,"Stop!"],[3407,3449,"Please!"],[3449,3561,"I didn't take it!"],[3674,3837,"Would you look at that."],[3912,3970,"How..."]],"40":[[8,183,"Nice try, you dirty thief."],[183,287,"Security!"],[304,454,"I didn't steal it."],[454,563,"You set me up."],[588,709,"You sneaky bitch!"],[742,817,"You're a liar."],[817,963,"Just like your dead daddy"],[963,1080,"who blew his brains out."],[1126,1272,"And now you're going to jail."],[1409,1497,"Evelyn, you're crazy."],[1497,1605,"You framed me."],[1605,1739,"Talk to me like that again."],[1739,1818,"And what?"],[2285,2394,"That ring doesn't even"],[2394,2506,"belong to you, Evelyn."],[2648,2773,"That was my mother's ring."],[2923,3136,"That was my heirloom in my safe,"],[3136,3240,"and I honestly didn't even know"],[3240,3324,"that you had it."],[3374,3520,"So who's the real thief here?"],[3599,3712,"I didn't steal anything, Beau."],[3712,3795,"She must have-"],[3795,3866,"I know, baby."]],"41":[[62,129,"Really?"],[283,350,"Of course."],[608,717,"I say, if Madison wants to"],[717,792,"keep the ring,"],[955,1038,"she should keep it."],[1338,1514,"And if anybody has a problem with that,"],[1514,1626,"they can talk to me."],[1643,1818,"She can't keep the ring."],[1818,1985,"She's a desperate slut!"],[1985,2118,"Oh, you like making a scene,"],[2118,2218,"don't you, Evelyn?"],[2243,2327,"Here, give me that."],[2731,2840,"Let's help her out, Maddie."],[3294,3424,"Final warning, Evelyn."],[3424,3570,"Leave us alone."],[3570,3674,"You don't want to piss off"],[3674,3862,"a cowboy and a city girl."],[3916,3987,"Trust me."]],"42":[[513,654,"You bitch."],[700,809,"Evelyn Campbell,"],[850,1026,"if you ever touch Madison again,"],[1059,1184,"I will personally ensure that"],[1184,1351,"not only will you not"],[1351,1564,"marry Maxi pad over here,"],[1564,1722,"you won't be able to pay another man"],[1722,1847,"in Texas to marry you."],[1918,2047,"Now get the fuck out of my sight."],[2131,2206,"We're done here!"],[2206,2314,"Oh, no."],[2314,2577,"That ring belongs to our family."],[2619,2736,"It's Max's."],[2827,2994,"You know what the will says, sister."],[3086,3232,"Remember whose ranch you live on."],[3570,3699,"You got some explaining to do."],[3799,3878,"You're coming home with me."],[4170,4350,"Not so fast, city skank."],[4508,4658,"Oh, shit!"]],"43":[[12,150,"Evelyn, what did you just do?"],[150,258,"No, no, no."],[258,442,"I meant to hit that thief."],[442,592,"She's just sleeping around"],[592,750,"to get out of all of her messes."],[750,859,"God damn it!"],[892,975,"Security!"],[1021,1151,"Take this goddamn criminal"],[1151,1251,"away right now."],[1259,1326,"No."],[1326,1376,"What?"],[1397,1514,"This is my party."],[1514,1597,"No!"],[1797,1885,"Beau, are you okay?"],[1885,1951,"Yeah, I'm okay."],[1951,2014,"I'm okay."],[2043,2114,"Are you okay?"],[2114,2173,"Yeah."],[2173,2227,"Yeah?"],[2298,2439,"Let's just get out of here."],[3478,3566,"Are you okay?"],[3636,3720,"I will be."],[3820,3924,"This is officially"],[3924,4116,"the worst day of my life."],[4200,4295,"Could be worse."],[4304,4375,"Oh, yeah?"],[4466,4529,"How?"]],"44":[[41,183,"Could still be at that party."],[775,921,"She got me good, though."],[1030,1167,"Are you okay?"],[1317,1468,"She hit you pretty hard."],[1676,1805,"I've been kicked by a young buck"],[1805,1931,"too many times to count."],[1960,2081,"She ain't got nothing on that."],[2281,2398,"Come on, city girl."],[2423,2523,"Let's get cleaned up."],[3516,3578,"Thank you."],[3661,3787,"I'm feeling a lot better now."],[4483,4554,"All right."],[4829,4913,"Strip."]],"45":[[12,75,"Strip."],[221,300,"Whoa."],[300,433,"Mr. Hayes."],[483,650,"At least buy me dinner first."],[784,905,"No, seriously."],[955,1046,"You're not tracking hay"],[1046,1151,"all through my ranch."],[1192,1301,"I might be Texan,"],[1301,1522,"but I'm sure as shit I am civilized."],[2727,2798,"Wait."],[2994,3144,"You saved me twice today."],[3290,3365,"Maddie."],[3478,3624,"Maybe it's time I repay the favor."],[3941,4045,"Stay, cowboy."]],"46":[[79,187,"You're impossible."],[504,617,"You love it, city girl."],[667,754,"You know I do."],[5397,5497,"Tell me you want it."],[5743,5822,"I want it."],[7678,7728,"Maddie!"],[7791,7857,"Maddie, Maddie."],[7932,8003,"Maddie, are you okay?"],[8003,8045,"Maddie."],[8045,8053,"Baby."]],"47":[[350,408,"Maddie."],[483,533,"Hey."],[663,792,"Hey baby, you awake now?"],[955,1076,"Did I die?"],[1251,1355,"No, you didn't die."],[1484,1584,"Not on my watch."],[1764,1839,"Miss Morris,"],[1868,2006,"you have a mild concussion."],[2060,2206,"So let this be a lesson to you,"],[2206,2293,"no more drinking."],[2318,2469,"Especially in your condition."],[2623,2698,"Don't worry doctor,"],[2698,2923,"I won't be drinking or concussed."],[2944,3044,"Or pregnant."],[3282,3457,"You're still pretty early on"],[3457,3553,"in your first trimester,"],[3553,3707,"so the baby's still safe for now."],[3782,3878,"Wait, baby?"],[3920,4004,"That can't be."],[4079,4316,"The only person I've been with is..."],[4500,4562,"Beau."]],"48":[[41,191,"I think I'm gonna pass out."],[191,237,"Maddie!"],[250,300,"Maddie!"],[329,367,"Maddie!"],[600,688,"Oh!"],[767,855,"Well, well."],[855,959,"Look who's back."],[1009,1088,"Now, how much of"],[1088,1197,"my hard-earned money"],[1197,1347,"did you burn through this time?"],[1368,1530,"Oh, only a small fortune."],[1530,1622,"Hmm."],[1622,1705,"That's my girl."],[1751,1851,"You deserve the best."],[2231,2298,"Sweetheart,"],[2339,2477,"why don't you go show your mother"],[2477,2527,"what you got?"],[2590,2644,"Okay."],[2686,2806,"Is everything okay?"],[2982,3061,"Of course."],[3182,3253,"Just business."],[3290,3340,"Okay."],[4108,4279,"You framed me, fraud."],[4441,4517,"How could you?"]],"49":[[4,141,"I can't go to prison, please."],[275,375,"What about my family?"],[400,500,"They don't deserve this."],[583,646,"My daughter"],[646,729,"doesn't deserve this!"],[867,917,"Madison."],[980,1026,"I,"],[1084,1167,"I'm sorry."],[1213,1297,"Uh..."],[1497,1564,"It's okay."],[1614,1755,"You should really go get some rest."],[1843,2068,"And just remember"],[2068,2323,"that I love you so much and"],[2423,2606,"everything that I'm doing"],[2635,2786,"is all for you, princess."],[2969,3048,"Go get some rest."],[3224,3282,"Okay."],[4108,4300,"Dad is going to love this watch"],[4300,4421,"for his birthday tomorrow."]],"50":[[1388,1451,"Daddy?"],[2652,2702,"Maddie!"],[2744,2831,"Maddie, shh, shh."],[2865,2927,"Baby, look at me."],[2927,2990,"You okay?"],[2990,3057,"You all right?"],[3057,3132,"What happened?"],[3207,3332,"Beau, I'm so scared."],[3332,3503,"I don't have anybody."],[3611,3691,"Oh, no, no."],[3691,3791,"That's not true, baby."],[3841,3912,"You have me."],[4020,4124,"I ain't going anywhere."]],"51":[[29,95,"You have me."],[204,312,"And I ain't going anywhere."],[633,821,"Hey, Maddie, are you okay?"],[900,971,"The doctor called me"],[971,1063,"and said you passed out"],[1063,1163,"and you hit your head."],[1226,1405,"Jesus, Maddie, I was terrified."],[1564,1730,"Wait, the doctor's called you?"],[1776,1885,"So, I'm your emergency"],[1885,1993,"contact, remember?"],[2014,2081,"Yeah, well,"],[2081,2214,"they ought to update that file."],[2281,2364,"Oh, yeah?"],[2489,2565,"And why is that?"],[2623,2773,"Because I'm the father of her child."],[2836,2890,"Wait."],[3086,3140,"What?"],[3203,3294,"You heard me all right."],[3465,3582,"So why don't you just leave."],[3624,3724,"Give us some space."],[3724,3824,"Let me take care of her."]],"52":[[50,116,"You should have"],[116,225,"told me yourself, Madison."],[258,483,"Please, let's not fight,"],[483,717,"let's just talk about this, guys."],[729,846,"Well, I'm telling you right now."],[846,950,"Leave Maddie alone."],[1026,1159,"So you're calling her Maddie now?"],[1197,1451,"I don't care who the father is."],[1476,1584,"How long have you even known her?"],[1634,1718,"A couple of months?"],[1797,1860,"I've known her since"],[1860,1951,"we were kids."],[1960,2210,"Yeah, well, we're having a kid now."],[2298,2373,"And this is none of"],[2373,2506,"your goddamn business, Taylor."],[2544,2635,"The hell it is!"],[2669,2781,"Are you guys even in love?"],[2848,3015,"I know your type, Beau Hayes."],[3094,3274,"The brooding manly man cowboy"],[3274,3324,"who has to put"],[3324,3428,"a toothpick in his mouth"],[3428,3545,"to seem dangerous."],[3595,3691,"But too bad he can't use"],[3691,3787,"that damn mouth of his"],[3787,3928,"to say how he really feels."],[4016,4116,"People like you,"],[4137,4262,"aren't capable of love."],[4262,4320,"Yeah?"],[4320,4375,"Yeah."],[4408,4462,"Is that right?"],[4462,4562,"Yes, that is right-"],[4700,4813,"Take it easy, little guy."]],"53":[[12,112,"We ain't doing this here."],[183,346,"Not in front of the mother of my child."],[404,471,"You hear me?"],[1530,1614,"Taylor, wait."],[1897,2031,"Are you serious?"],[2031,2168,"Why would you do that?"],[2168,2268,"He's a friend!"],[2310,2406,"He's like family!"],[2406,2469,"Family?"],[2560,2640,"And what am I then?"],[2823,2977,"It just doesn't make any sense."],[3007,3119,"Somebody had to tell him."],[3128,3244,"Maybe if he wasn't sniffing around"],[3244,3378,"like a goddamn lost puppy,"],[3436,3570,"he wouldn't have to find out this way."],[3595,3862,"Oh my God, Beau, are you serious?"],[3862,3999,"He's just a friend!"],[3999,4079,"Friends?"],[4229,4362,"Last time I checked, honey,"],[4412,4550,"just friends isn't the first person"],[4550,4633,"that shows up"],[4633,4738,"when you have an emergency"],[4738,4854,"at the goddamn hospital."],[4954,5080,"God, why are you"],[5080,5238,"so jealous of Taylor?"],[5238,5334,"Because he thinks he knows you"],[5334,5397,"better than me."],[5397,5476,"And that ain't true."],[5522,5663,"Because I'm the father of this baby."],[5718,5830,"And he ain't the man for you."],[5843,5926,"Oh."],[5926,6039,"And you are?"],[6039,6143,"Goddamn right I am."],[7307,7453,"And I want you to move in with me."],[7570,7670,"Move in?"]],"54":[[50,175,"You're having my child, Maddie."],[300,400,"Our baby."],[500,583,"And you're not going to be living"],[583,667,"with another man."],[1034,1167,"I want to take care of you."],[1167,1263,"I want to protect you."],[1343,1468,"And the doctor said that..."],[1655,1718,"we need to get some"],[1718,1805,"real food in you."],[1976,2047,"And I want to take you on a"],[2047,2131,"proper date."],[2239,2331,"You hear me, city girl?"],[2419,2489,"Is that alright?"],[3123,3303,"So, let me get this straight."],[3303,3478,"You basically extorted me"],[3478,3636,"into moving in with you"],[3636,3887,"and now you're holding me hostage"],[3941,4029,"at your backwoods"],[4029,4116,"makeshift restaurant."],[4170,4266,"Relax, city girl."],[4295,4371,"It's just dinner."],[4371,4546,"It's not an episode of Criminal Minds."],[4596,4671,"Debatable."]],"55":[[108,154,"Come on."],[196,283,"You gotta try it."],[329,412,"You're in Texas now."],[529,579,"You gotta learn"],[579,771,"how to eat like a true southerner."],[971,1117,"I'm supposed to eat this with my hands?"],[1163,1255,"Yes, princess."],[1351,1409,"I'll teach you."],[1564,1626,"Going to grab it