owgirl boots."]],"59":[[33,125,"I figure it's time"],[125,208,"that you got to start"],[208,312,"looking like you belong here,"],[312,404,"not so city girl."],[529,809,"When I saw you line dancing like a pro,"],[834,909,"I knew you had to have"],[909,1092,"a real pair of boots."],[1242,1334,"And a real man."],[1601,1714,"And I want to be that man."],[1830,2072,"But your nephew,"],[2231,2381,"Max is my ex."],[2381,2544,"Shit, don't worry about him."],[2544,2590,"Just..."],[2765,2823,"just,"],[2998,3086,"tell me one thing."],[3399,3524,"How do you feel about me?"]],"60":[[458,642,"I've fallen for you too, cowboy."],[863,917,"Yeah?"],[1255,1351,"Then stay with me."],[1380,1509,"Let's make a family together."],[1739,1960,"Yes, Beau, but..."],[2077,2223,"what about your family?"],[2385,2523,"What about Max,"],[2523,2677,"and Kate,"],[2677,2806,"and Evelyn,"],[2806,2877,"and-"],[2877,2936,"Whatever,"],[2936,3032,"don't worry about them."],[3073,3182,"I'm going to deal with them."],[3182,3265,"That's what I do."],[3386,3524,"I want to care for you."],[3524,3632,"I want to protect you."],[3753,3828,"From everything."],[4020,4120,"What's everything?"]],"61":[[175,308,"You know I own this town, right?"],[383,454,"Well,"],[517,592,"I thought it'd looked"],[592,658,"pretty sketchy"],[658,729,"if an out-of-towner"],[729,850,"was working at the bar."],[925,984,"You know..."],[1213,1309,"I'm friends with the sheriff"],[1309,1505,"and I had him look into a few things."],[1626,1772,"You had a background check"],[1772,1835,"done on me?"],[2031,2139,"How dare you?"],[2139,2427,"Maddie, it's not like that, alright?"],[2427,2515,"Look, I just..."],[2590,2744,"I had him look into your daddy's case."],[2744,3057,"And honestly, shit just ain't adding up."],[3211,3361,"Maddie, look at me."],[3449,3499,"Come here."],[3574,3611,"Come on."],[3778,3862,"You trust me, right?"]],"62":[[33,112,"You trust me, right?"],[462,592,"Your daddy didn't do the things"],[592,696,"that they said he did."],[809,909,"He was framed."],[1217,1313,"How do you know?"],[1372,1493,"You know, I know the sheriff"],[1493,1593,"and I got connections"],[1593,1634,"with people"],[1634,1760,"that look into things"],[1760,1931,"and stuff that folks"],[1931,2031,"don't want to get found."],[2152,2385,"But who would frame him?"],[2385,2544,"Honestly, I have no idea, but..."],[2627,2731,"Maddie, I can promise you"],[2731,2844,"that I ain't gonna stop"],[2844,2932,"until I find out."],[3265,3386,"No one's ever tried to"],[3386,3503,"clear his name before."],[3749,3832,"You know,"],[3958,4079,"I ain't just anyone, am I."],[4262,4366,"There's something else."],[4471,4646,"I know this may be crazy, but..."],[4696,4888,"I got some connections"],[4888,5034,"at the hospital, too, and..."],[5067,5196,"I want you to talk to your mom."],[5292,5380,"I got her on the phone."],[5488,5597,"Wait, she's awake?"],[5697,5809,"Yeah, you can't see her, but..."],[5976,6039,"Mama?"],[6060,6239,"Oh, my baby girl."],[6239,6356,"I'm okay."],[6356,6489,"The treatment is working."],[6489,6715,"I feel stronger every day."],[6748,6965,"I can't wait to see you."],[7073,7178,"I'll see you soon."],[7178,7253,"I love you."],[7290,7424,"Love you, too, sweetheart."],[7732,7824,"Thank you."],[7828,7887,"Thank you,"],[7887,7928,"I..."],[8028,8195,"I don't know how I can repay you."],[8420,8475,"I do."]],"63":[[83,429,"Look, I know this has been crazy."],[450,538,"And this isn't the life"],[538,746,"that you envisioned."],[880,955,"But you're mine."],[1013,1084,"You understand that?"],[1668,1768,"I want to do this right."],[2214,2298,"I want to put this back"],[2298,2394,"where it belongs."],[2706,2765,"Marry me."],[3011,3123,"What do you say?"],[3199,3328,"It's a perfect fit."],[3745,3820,"I love you."],[4170,4262,"I love you, too."]],"64":[[437,592,"You never see stars like this"],[592,688,"in the city."],[1217,1334,"You know what that ring means,"],[1334,1422,"don't you, darling?"],[1689,1989,"That I'm yours, that you're mine."],[2152,2202,"And that you're gonna"],[2202,2327,"stay here in Texas."],[2627,2727,"You can see the stars"],[2727,2823,"whenever you'd like."],[3023,3098,"I love him,"],[3219,3370,"but am I really going to move"],[3370,3516,"to Texas?"],[4583,4688,"I love him."],[4808,5000,"I'm going to stay in Texas"],[5000,5092,"for our family."],[5167,5271,"I've made my decision."]],"65":[[454,508,"We need to postpone"],[508,567,"the wedding."],[696,800,"Excuse me?"],[800,896,"The whole town is talking."],[896,1055,"Between you trying to frame Madison"],[1055,1130,"and Beau making a scene,"],[1130,1222,"it's bad for business."],[1267,1334,"Beau says he's gonna stop"],[1334,1397,"funding our ranch"],[1397,1472,"if you're around."],[1472,1518,"No way!"],[1518,1659,"Our wedding date is set!"],[1972,2093,"Oh, honey."],[2156,2302,"There ain't going to be no wedding."],[2302,2389,"It's over."],[2410,2569,"I just got off the phone with Beau"],[2569,2831,"and he has agreed to fund the ranch."],[2873,2948,"What the hell"],[2948,3057,"does that have to do with me?"],[3094,3319,"Well, it means we don't need"],[3319,3432,"your family's money."],[3432,3591,"And that was the deal."],[3624,3741,"You bring the money"],[3741,3962,"and you get to marry my son."],[4012,4087,"But now?"],[4179,4275,"I guess we're done here."],[4412,4491,"I'm going to go give"],[4491,4575,"that little gold digger"],[4575,4817,"exactly what she deserves."],[4829,5025,"A lesson, country style."],[5050,5134,"This ain't over."]],"66":[[2085,2327,"Can I really just leave my city life"],[2327,2510,"and move to Texas for Beau?"],[2623,2752,"Catching flies, city girl?"],[2861,2932,"More like wondering"],[2932,3048,"if you actually do any work"],[3048,3219,"or just stand there looking pretty."],[3482,3545,"You shouldn't be working"],[3545,3628,"in your condition."],[3803,3987,"Beau, I just collected eggs."],[4033,4216,"I'm not breaking in wild stallions."],[4283,4358,"Maybe later."],[4466,4558,"When you came to Texas,"],[4558,4717,"you were a spoiled little city girl."]],"67":[[45,129,"Now look at you,"],[129,187,"working,"],[241,367,"wearing the boots."],[525,671,"I guess Texas is really rubbing off"],[671,738,"on you, huh?"],[784,867,"I guess it is."],[1096,1167,"Alright then."],[1276,1405,"I'm gonna in and take a rinse."],[1493,1614,"Holler if you need anything."],[1951,2106,"With a man like that,"],[2106,2306,"I can definitely live here forever."],[2327,2435,"I just need to tell him."],[3378,3511,"After all we've been through,"],[3578,3674,"she's leaving me"],[3674,3791,"to go back to New York?"],[3837,3887,"No."],[3949,4037,"No, I have to show her."],[4070,4187,"I have to tell her"],[4225,4525,"that we're meant to be, Madison Morris."]],"68":[[508,613,"Madison Morris!"],[700,896,"This is all your fault!"],[1113,1201,"My stomach!"],[1234,1326,"Get her, Evelyn."],[1426,1505,"My baby."],[1564,1630,"Baby?"],[1676,1760,"You're pregnant?"],[1785,2022,"What a desperate city whore."],[2077,2223,"You are the reason my fiancé"],[2223,2314,"called off the wedding."],[2327,2439,"His family was supposed to"],[2439,2548,"be mine!"],[2548,2619,"Hold her back."],[2660,2815,"I'll teach this skank a lesson."],[2852,2923,"What the hell?"],[3073,3178,"I don't want Max."],[3178,3269,"You can keep him."],[3332,3420,"You're only saying that"],[3420,3516,"because you crawled in bed"],[3516,3566,"with his uncle"],[3566,3699,"and got knocked up, didn't you?"],[3999,4166,"Huh, good idea."]],"69":[[312,392,"You think you can just"],[392,538,"waltz into this town"],[538,692,"and sleep your way into my family?"],[734,930,"I didn't waltz anywhere."],[1071,1109,"You're the one"],[1109,1259,"who's been coming after me."],[1259,1330,"Framing me."],[1330,1430,"Humiliating me."],[1459,1710,"I just care about Beau and our baby."],[1826,1947,"If you're with child,"],[1985,2052,"then you're going to need"],[2052,2168,"a whole lot of nutrition."],[2356,2477,"Hope bird flu doesn't"],[2477,2581,"get you, tramp!"],[3490,3641,"I can't eat raw egg,"],[3641,3732,"I'm pregnant!"],[3732,3795,"Come on,"],[3795,3933,"slut's like you like to swallow,"],[3933,4020,"so swallow it!"],[4091,4212,"Beau, save me!"],[4212,4283,"Help!"],[4329,4404,"Help!"],[4462,4537,"Madison!"],[4571,4792,"Eat the egg or else, city skank!"],[4917,4984,"Hey!"],[5146,5296,"Evelyn, what the fuck are you doing?"]],"70":[[8,145,"The fuck are you doing, Evelyn?"],[321,379,"Maddie, come here baby."],[483,542,"Are you okay?"],[625,688,"Come here, baby."],[980,1030,"You all right?"],[1063,1109,"Look at me."],[1109,1163,"You okay?"],[1418,1501,"You have five seconds"],[1501,1639,"to get the fuck off my property."],[1672,1822,"Before I personally put your ass"],[1822,1989,"on the next train out of Texas!"],[2060,2285,"Actually, Beau, that's a good idea."],[2381,2439,"We should put her"],[2439,2527,"on the next flight out."],[2581,2865,"If I see your face again, screw Texas,"],[2911,2986,"I'll make sure that"],[2986,3107,"I never see your face"],[3107,3240,"in the South ever again!"],[3374,3449,"You get me?"],[4425,4554,"It's horse shit!"],[4562,4708,"Somebody help me!"]],"71":[[16,66,"It really looks like"],[66,175,"Miss Pageant Queen fell off."],[200,291,"Ew."],[291,354,"Looks like you're having"],[354,492,"a shitty day, Ev."],[571,734,"Oh my god!"],[875,971,"Now get out of here!"],[1155,1305,"I'm tired of your shit, Evelyn."],[1676,1726,"Hey!"],[1843,1910,"Don't think I don't know"],[1910,2006,"what y'all did here."],[2064,2127,"And if you ever show up"],[2127,2202,"in my establishment"],[2202,2243,"again,"],[2243,2298,"I swear to God,"],[2298,2414,"there's gonna be hell to pay."],[2494,2577,"Nobody messes with"],[2577,2656,"Madison Morris."],[2848,2948,"Now get out of my sight."],[3032,3086,"Now!"],[3274,3336,"You okay?"],[3374,3436,"Yeah."],[3453,3499,"You sure?"],[3520,3582,"Yeah."],[4250,4295,"Hey."],[4383,4446,"Come sit."],[4583,4662,"Excuse me?"]],"72":[[41,137,"I'm gonna brush your hair."],[4254,4362,"I can't, um..."],[4575,4704,"I can't keep doing this."],[4783,4863,"What does he mean?"],[4900,5055,"Is he leaving me?"]],"73":[[588,763,"I can't keep falling for you."],[809,900,"I don't know if you're..."],[1080,1217,"itching to go back to the city."],[1343,1426,"But if you tell me"],[1426,1534,"that's what you want to do,"],[1576,1647,"I'll let you go."],[1835,1926,"That's not home."],[2131,2214,"Not anymore."],[2427,2644,"Home, Beau Hayes,"],[2786,2940,"is where our family is."],[3032,3136,"It's where you are."],[3490,3616,"But your flight home jar,"],[3670,3728,"it's gone."],[3908,4049,"I know you bought a plane ticket."],[4450,4550,"You don't know"],[4550,4688,"as much as you think you do."],[4900,4992,"Wait here, cowboy."]],"74":[[1267,1422,"I used that money to buy this outfit"],[1422,1555,"for you as a surprise."],[1634,1760,"Not plane tickets."],[1976,2081,"Looks like the city girl's"],[2081,2193,"gonna stay in Texas."],[2394,2565,"Ready to be a cowgirl just for you."],[4070,4216,"You know I always wanted to see you"],[4216,4346,"in an outfit like this."],[4433,4500,"But now..."],[5021,5251,"I just want to see you take it off."]],"75":[[508,721,"Mama, Max doesn't love me."],[825,955,"He's still in love with Madison."],[1046,1180,"Marriage ain't about love."],[1305,1418,"Love fades."],[1564,1743,"Money lasts."],[1964,2248,"Right now, Max's family has money"],[2248,2385,"that keeps this house running."],[2773,2957,"How is it, that Madison"],[2957,3140,"has snatched up Beau Hayes,"],[3140,3236,"and you can hardly keep"],[3236,3365,"Max's eyes on you?"],[3395,3478,"I have the perfect way"],[3478,3616,"to get rid of Madison Morris."],[3653,3799,"I'm gonna marry into that family."],[3853,4012,"And how do you plan on doing that?"],[4045,4229,"Well, Momma,"],[4333,4462,"you and I are the only ones"],[4462,4512,"who know what happened"],[4512,4617,"to Madison's dad."],[4642,4779,"You framed him for fraud."],[4808,4909,"So he'd kill himself."],[5009,5117,"And I'm sure"],[5117,5280,"Madison would love to know"],[5280,5543,"how her dear daddy died."]],"76":[[1509,1584,"Hello?"],[1589,1693,"Miss Morris?"],[1701,1951,"This is Agent Diane Carter with the FBI."],[1964,2064,"I wanted to update you"],[2064,2218,"on your father's case."],[2218,2277,"I..."],[2369,2544,"I thought the case was closed."],[2544,2736,"That's what they wanted you to think."],[2773,2844,"Can we meet?"],[2865,3011,"I think we should talk in person."],[3061,3157,"Absolutely."],[3194,3336,"Meet me at the Saddle Saloon."],[3357,3420,"Now."],[3574,3649,"Thank you."],[3703,3858,"Agent Carter, thank you."],[4337,4529,"Madison, what are you doing here?"],[4529,4688,"We don't open for hours."],[4688,4796,"And I'm under strict orders"],[4796,4871,"from Mr. Hayes"],[4871,5000,"that you're not to be working."],[5030,5205,"I'm just meeting someone to talk to."],[5284,5438,"Ah, that checks out."],[5484,5563,"Somebody's been coming by"],[5563,5634,"waiting for you."]],"77":[[300,362,"Hey, Maddie."],[487,554,"Hey, Tay."],[1368,1476,"So..."],[1555,1659,"y'all moved out?"],[1739,1801,"Madison,"],[1914,2064,"I'm only gonna say this once."],[2339,2427,"I love you."],[2590,2715,"I've always loved you."],[2790,2869,"Leave Beau."],[2969,3048,"Be with me."],[3140,3386,"Taylor, I can't do this right now."],[3465,3511,"Okay?"],[3511,3774,"I love you too, but..."],[3849,3933,"as a friend."]],"78":[[79,171,"And you love him?"],[396,492,"Like a soulmate."],[567,725,"He's not the right fit for you."],[880,1001,"But he is!"],[1184,1267,"And if you were really"],[1267,1330,"my best friend,"],[1330,1443,"you'd understand,"],[1443,1488,"but..."],[1589,1643,"Look, I..."],[1668,1739,"I'm waiting for"],[1739,1922,"a really important meeting right now,"],[1922,1981,"so I-"],[1981,2077,"So, I'll go."],[2185,2218,"You don't wanna"],[2218,2318,"see me around anyway."],[2448,2523,"Don't worry."],[2619,2690,"I won't interfere"],[2690,2790,"with your perfect life."],[2861,2927,"Taylor!"],[3211,3253,"Great."],[3382,3465,"Madison Morris?"],[3516,3595,"Agent Carter."],[3620,3682,"Not quite."],[3695,3737,"Hey!"],[3745,3795,"What?"]],"79":[[1697,1785,"Maddie."],[1830,1989,"Madison was kidnapped!"],[1989,2106,"The hell are you talking about?"],[2147,2369,"I swear, I don't know who it was,"],[2369,2502,"but this guy, just..."],[2502,2602,"he grabbed Madison"],[2602,2706,"and threw her into his van."],[2706,2773,"And you just happened"],[2773,2823,"to be there?"],[2861,2907,"How do I know"],[2907,3036,"you ain't got nothing to do with it?"],[3036,3144,"I wouldn't be coming to you"],[3144,3286,"if I had any other choice."],[3361,3445,"If I was involved,"],[3445,3582,"why would I bring her phone to you?"],[3666,3807,"We both love Madison,"],[3887,3983,"which is why we need to"],[3983,4112,"find her right now."],[4112,4270,"Did you see anyone else go in the van?"],[4454,4562,"No one I recognized."],[4650,4733,"Just two women,"],[4733,4863,"probably mother and daughter."],[4900,5050,"The youngest had red hair."],[5050,5125,"Red hair?"],[5125,5230,"Are you fucking kidding me?"],[5230,5296,"That's Evelyn!"],[5296,5351,"Let's go!"],[5376,5422,"Come on!"]],"80":[[408,513,"You tricked me."],[538,688,"Ain't that hard, city slicker."],[696,754,"Why?"],[804,938,"Why are you doing this?"],[988,1092,"Oh, Madison."],[1151,1213,"Why?"],[1247,1409,"Because you ruined my life!"],[1468,1555,"You won every pageant"],[1555,1659,"when we were kids."],[1659,1805,"And then you took Max."],[1805,1881,"And now Beau?"],[1906,2052,"Oh, you're not gonna win this one."],[2060,2277,"I'm not trying to win anything."],[2277,2356,"I just wanted to know"],[2356,2469,"what happened to my father."],[2548,2677,"It actually wasn't that hard."],[2706,2844,"My clever mama"],[2844,2998,"framed your dumb daddy,"],[2998,3148,"so that Max would dump you"],[3148,3332,"and I could marry into his family."],[3495,3603,"You framed him?"],[3645,3753,"Mhmm."],[3916,4041,"He was my dad!"],[4145,4270,"He was my hero!"],[4270,4333,"You,"],[4333,4600,"you took him for some money?"],[4600,4704,"He was in our way."],[4742,4904,"Just some dirty trash."],[4904,5034,"And we took care of him."],[5063,5251,"And now it's your turn."],[5263,5367,"Here's how it's gonna go."],[5422,5534,"You're gonna call Beau."],[5572,5659,"And you're gonna tell him"],[5659,5772,"that you never loved him."],[5772,5885,"And that you're leaving him."],[6010,6068,"I won't."],[6068,6206,"You will."],[6235,6373,"Or else I have somebody"],[6373,6468,"at the hospital"],[6468,6585,"that'll make your mama meet"],[6585,6710,"your daddy in heaven."],[6710,6781,"Hold her."],[6940,7057,"Don't touch me!"],[7086,7165,"Oh, Madison."],[7211,7323,"You have no choice."],[7349,7432,"You lost."],[7461,7603,"Now do what I say or else!"],[7603,7703,"Or else what?"]],"81":[[145,241,"Or else what?"],[329,387,"Beau."],[546,600,"Taylor?"],[767,829,"Oh!"],[880,942,"No!"],[1109,1205,"You alright, baby?"],[1205,1263,"You okay?"],[1297,1338,"Yeah?"],[1351,1401,"Yeah."],[1518,1614,"That's it, Evelyn."],[1655,1743,"You're done here."],[1814,1922,"You're done in Texas."],[1956,2018,"What?"],[2072,2277,"Her mother framed my father."],[2306,2406,"And she helped."],[2431,2519,"You lying bitch."],[2519,2610,"You have no proof."],[2610,2681,"Proof?"],[2727,2827,"You want proof?"],[2827,2927,"How's this for you?"],[2957,3053,"My clever mama"],[3053,3199,"framed your dumb daddy,"],[3199,3353,"so that Max would dump you,"],[3353,3570,"and I could marry into his family."],[3582,3707,"This video is live,"],[3745,3928,"seen by the whole goddamn town."],[3987,4087,"You're done here, Evelyn."],[4233,4429,"Oh, and uh, your family farm?"],[4542,4637,"Let's just say..."],[4700,4775,"Well, shit."],[4808,4884,"I own it now."],[4892,4917,"No."]],"82":[[0,112,"I got one more gift for you."],[137,183,"Come here."],[425,554,"What the hell is this?"],[583,696,"A citizen's arrest."],[825,925,"I didn't tell you about the time"],[925,1042,"that I was a bounty hunter?"],[1146,1217,"You're going to jail."],[1259,1363,"Oh, and uh..."],[1405,1480,"don't worry,"],[1593,1701,"you won't be alone."],[1876,1964,"Susan Campbell."],[2072,2173,"You're under arrest."],[2264,2398,"For fraud and conspiracy."],[2427,2527,"That so?"],[2669,2773,"And who, pray tell,"],[2773,2902,"made up that little story?"],[2927,2990,"Your daughter."],[3094,3240,"She confessed everything."],[3315,3420,"Your time is up."],[3486,3636,"That ungrateful little-"],[3636,3682,"Ma'am."],[3741,3841,"You can either come quietly."],[4008,4108,"Or we can make a scene"],[4108,4279,"in front of all your fancy neighbors."]],"83":[[196,287,"Easy now. - Got it?"],[392,467,"There you go."],[525,608,"You're comfortable?"],[608,675,"I'm good,"],[675,713,"thank you."],[713,750,"Yeah?"],[759,796,"Yeah."],[905,971,"There you go."],[1038,1176,"You're both amazing."],[1205,1284,"Thank you for"],[1284,1418,"clearing Richard's name."],[1493,1618,"I'm sure your father"],[1618,1760,"is resting easy now."],[1864,2027,"As proud of you as ever."],[2173,2406,"I just wish he was here"],[2406,2515,"to see you marry"],[2515,2656,"this handsome gentleman."],[2727,2798,"Mom!"],[3019,3140,"Well, she's going to make"],[3140,3274,"a beautiful bride, Leslie."],[3636,3703,"Taylor!"],[3745,4070,"Hey, I just came to say goodbye."]],"84":[[66,191,"I'm heading to New York."],[262,417,"I bought this as a souvenir"],[417,642,"of our trials and tribulations here."],[771,867,"Taylor, um,"],[1038,1151,"I can't believe you're leaving."],[1313,1430,"I'm sorry."],[1463,1722,"Hey, don't be."],[1860,1931,"It's okay."],[2122,2273,"I see that you're in good hands now."],[2377,2460,"I'll be around."],[2598,2669,"Always."],[3032,3119,"You take care of her."],[3240,3307,"Always."],[3361,3470,"See you around, Taylor."],[4266,4383,"Let's get you comfy."],[4721,4771,"Madison."]],"85":[[33,112,"Max!"],[145,221,"I've been looking for you,"],[221,275,"I just,"],[325,400,"I just wanted,"],[508,558,"I wanted to say"],[558,709,"I'm sorry for everything."],[759,925,"The way I treated you, it was terrible."],[925,1046,"And you didn't deserve that."],[1088,1142,"Well,"],[1301,1526,"I'm not sure I can forgive you, but..."],[1643,1710,"thank you."],[1843,1893,"Hey!"],[1947,2035,"Easy there, nephew."],[2152,2227,"After all,"],[2227,2364,"she's my fiancée now."],[2431,2540,"Which makes her,"],[2585,2665,"your aunt."],[2911,3053,"So don't disrespect her,"],[3053,3190,"or I'll have to discipline you."],[3324,3424,"You know very well"],[3424,3603,"what I'm capable of, Maxipad."],[4233,4316,"Fiancée?"],[4475,4592,"I like the sound of that."],[4654,4829,"I like the sound of that too, city girl."]],"86":[[508,621,"Hey there, little cowboy."],[1109,1276,"Isn't our baby boy a real beaut,"],[1276,1347,"Mrs. Hayes?"],[1426,1568,"He sure is, Mr. Hayes."],[1718,1818,"Just like his daddy."],[1926,1997,"I don't know."],[2047,2243,"He looks more like his mama, city girl."],[2548,2711,"Beau, you can't call me that anymore."],[2869,2911,"What?"],[2986,3103,"It's country girl now."],[3390,3449,"Of course."],[3745,3883,"You're my country girl now."],[4429,4537,"Forever, cowboy."],[4671,4779,"Forever."]]}